verse = \lyricmode {
  By day he gave a cloud to lead and guide them;
with fie -- ry light did he all night pro -- vide them.
Drink as a -- bun -- dant as the seas he gave them;
he split the rocks, and springs welled up to save them.
From bar -- ren crags he made fresh foun -- tains burst,
and riv -- ers flowed to quench his peo -- ple's thirst.
}
